description: Philips O'Neill's SHO2200 THE TREAD is an extremely tough in-ear headphone. Acoustically tuned to be loud with deep bass while delivering clear audio for calls. Extra tough with reinforced connectors and metal housing to withstand impacts.
title: Philips O'Neill SHO2200BK/28 The Tread In-Ear Headphones - Black (Discontinued by Manufacturer)
